name: puppethandandelions
description:
is this a flowery donuts or is it a flower from another dimension?
Fractals are sometimes combined with evolutionary algorithms, either by iteratively choosing good-looking specimens in a set of random variations of a fractal artwork
and producing new variations. In this collection I tried to have a diffrrent perspective to objects and forms in a fractal way
to simulate some emotions which dependent on your perspective to the piece, some feels gross some love the flower...
made by Maya and render it with Arnold..cheers
